ANTI-MILITARY FLATTOP ☮️
Step into the groovy vibes of the 70s with this authentic flattop hairstyle.
It’s not a military style, it’s a haircut for the the most clever people.
One of my beloved customers, who happens to be a flattop enthusiast, shared an interesting story with me. He revealed that his father and grandfather, both esteemed professors at the university, always sported the flattop haircut.
And guess what? It’s not just any ordinary haircut – it’s a symbol of intelligence and sharpness!
.
📍Salt Lake City, Utah 🇺🇸
.
#barberworld #barberlife #babershop #barber #flattop #barbereducation
